comment_data.body: Version bump shouldn't be there in the first place. It should be in it's own commit.
Moved version bump to a separate commit.
And yes, 0.0.7 was manually created, and still broken.

commit.message:
Add benchmark and test modules to extra-source-files.

`cabal sdist` doesn't include bench and test modules.

Fixes #20
Fixes #25
